TO: STANLEY KUBRICK1

CC, 2 pp.

San Remo, Italy





December 31, 1959

Dear Mr. Kubrick,

We have just received your letter of December 21, addressed to Milan. In the meanwhile Mr. Lazar2 has been in touch with you and with us. We are now waiting for his call but my husband welcomes this opportunity to sum up the situation in a letter from us to you.

